&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3>CROSS JOIN&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="cross-join">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#cross-join" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>두 테이블의 모든 가능한 조합을 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
